Text.Value: *A timeless space, bounded, compressed in a fold - a pocket of Astral Plane.*

EditorData.logicalname: INCLUSION ADDED AT START TO LOCK PLAYERS EARLY

Text.Value: *The concentration of psionic force is small but unmistakable - this must be a pocket of the Astral Plane.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] Player stumbles as they appeared at new location, steadies themselves, then looks around them
EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Shot of player looking out into the Astral plane, a little bit off balance from having been teleported, wide shots to introduce and establish location.
EditorData.SFXTags: [WI] Audio support as the players and peanuts teleporting and landing on astral plane
EditorData.VFXTags: [WI] VFX support showing the players and peanuts teleporting onto astral plane, air distortion effects perhaps

Text.Value: It's... beautiful. Gods, what a sight.
Quite an oddity to behold... but not without beauty, either.
It's quite beautiful - though dangerous things often are.

EditorData.logicalname: INCLUSION ADDED AT START TO LOCK PLAYERS EARLY

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: At peak speed, a bright white light engulfs you and the room. Fade to white.
EditorData.SFXTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] High pitch whine as magic builds up
EditorData.VFXTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] Light particles as magical energy buildup crescendoes

Text.Value: Incredible - space, unfettered from time. The Astral Plane, just as I've dreamt it.
*Heat pulses out of the Astral Prism as it begins to flower.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: [ChrisD] Artifacts activated, each plates open up and moves around. Its movement gets more intensifies overtime., [ChrisD] Player startles as soon as the artifact glows and opens up.
EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: The gaps between the 'plates' of the artefact glow, and the 'plates' of the artefact fracture out and begin to move, shifting faster and faster.
EditorData.SFXTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] Magical hum intensifies as artifact transforms
EditorData.VFXTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] Glow shining through from between the artifact's pieces

Text.Value: Boundless, timeless - like every dream that ever was, stitched together. It is home.
Extraordinary - like a waking dream. Where have we gotten to?
Incredible. It feels like nowhere and everywhere, all at once.
*The place is expansive, beautiful, but unfamiliar. Could all this have fit inside the artefact?*

EditorData.AnimationTags: [AMN][GUS-209394] Player reaches out to touch artifact
EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: The player reaches out to touch the artefact, which is floating above the planecaster.

Text.Value: Quite a sight. Though I'm not quite sure what sight exactly.
Can't believe what I'm seeing. This place is beautiful.
*A feeling of belonging stirs within you - a fold in reality, a pocket of the Astral Plane.*

EditorData.NodeContext: Looking out over the astral plane, as if you've been transported to space
A pause before the second beautiful. "Strange, but ... beautiful."

Synopsis: Once the player has gathered their party and the artefact has been placed on the planecaster in gameplay, this dialogue plays and the party is teleported to the Astral Prism where the party reacts to the environment.
